trans-unit.source: Defines values for specifying the parts of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell"></xref> that are to be painted.
trans-unit.target: 部分を指定する値を定義、 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell"> </xref>を描画する必要があります。

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used by the protected <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.Paint%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method and by handlers for the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellPainting>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPrePaint>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPostPaint> events of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> control.
trans-unit.target: この列挙を使用で保護された<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.Paint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>メソッド用のハンドラーで、 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellPainting>、 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPrePaint>、および<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPostPaint>のイベント、<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>コントロール</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView></xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPostPaint></xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPrePaint></xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellPainting></xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.Paint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。
